description:
Will is 19 years old. He's working on his General Ed at a community college before moving onto university.
He was on several sports teams in high school, but only plays recreationally now in order to work and study.
He has a girlfriend, whom he has been dating since high school. They've discussed marriage, but he isn't sure.
"I want to wait until I'm out of school," he said. "You never know how things will work out."
Apparently, she won't let him fuck her up the ass. So maybe that's the deal breaker!
title: Will
